	(text "DMN3009SSS\n-> 1.8W max: 160ma 5.5mOhm  0.15mW power while on\n-> Switching losses unknown.\n-> Max current 8 x 80mA = 0,64A Power = I^2*R = 0.64^2 * 0.0055 = 2.25mW\n-> Smaller power setup 8 x 60mA = "
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 20.32 18.288 0)
